desc: Enjoy the perfect healthy, delicious, snack. Veronica's Health Crunch is handmade in small batches. Almonds, pecans, organic sunflower seeds, organic pumpkin seeds, raw honey, cranberries. Comes in four flavors: original, cinnamon apple cranberry, banana chocolate walnut, sweet cherry heat.

layout.text: An all natural blend of nuts, lightly sweetened with honey. It has almonds, walnuts, pecans and pumpkin seeds, dried sweetened cranberries, and unsweetened shredded coconut.
